data.description: Recently updated with a blend of style and practicality, this welcoming home in Sarah's Creek offers a comfortable and turn-key living experience. Key improvements include fresh interior & exterior paint, updated hardware and fixtures, newer water heater (2022), brand new roof, and a new HVAC system to be installed this week, ensuring long-term reliability.    Inside, the home features a fresh, modern look with newly painted walls and kitchen cabinets, new cabinet hardware, doorknobs, and ceiling fans updated in matte black throughout, adding a touch of sophistication. The primary suite is enhanced by an updated bathroom with garden tub, and sizable walk-in closet outfitted with custom shelving, creating a cozy and functional space. Conveniently located with easy access to I-35, HEB, and downtown Pflugerville's amenities, this home is ideal for those seeking a balance of contemporary updates and everyday comfort.
